name: Order a product

steps.name: Given I am on the inventory page
When I sort products from high price to low price
And I add the highest priced product to the cart
And I click on the cart
And I click the Continue button
Then I verify the total amount for the added item is "$49.99"
When I click the Finish button
Then the "Thank You" header is shown in the Checkout Complete page

fullName: Login and Product Ordering: Order a product
